item.title: Website for my server and ip help!
item.dc:creator: @ksv ksv
item.description:
@ksv wrote:

goto http://www.dot.tk, enter ur ip adress, ex: - http://(youripadress). after that press “next”

  • now choose ur website name, it can be whatever u want. ex: yourname(.tk) remember .tk!
    then scroll down and u’ll see some characters, type them into the box under.
    Now, scroll down …
    and u will see 2 choises …
    i recommend you to choose the " email required ".
    then sign up.

How to find ur ip?

goto start > run > cmd > ipconfig - and there ull see ur ip(;
(thats the 1 u put in Dot.tk field.)
